[Ladypool] You kidding me?
Every Deadpool has a Peter.

2483
01:43:45,947 --> 01:43:48,155
[Cowboypool] Shit.
Peter's a goddamn legend

2484
01:43:48,238 --> 01:43:49,613
in every Deadpool's world.

2485
01:43:49,697 --> 01:43:52,072
Peter-<i>san. Hai.</i>

2486
01:43:52,155 --> 01:43:53,697
[Deadpools cheering]

2487
