[Peter laughs]

2488
01:43:59,280 --> 01:44:01,322
[Deadpools chanting]
Peter. Peter. Peter.

2489
01:44:01,405 --> 01:44:04,697
Peter. Peter. Peter.
Peter. Peter. Peter.

2490
01:44:04,780 --> 01:44:06,905
- Peter. Peter. Peter.
- [Peter laughing]

2491
01:44:07,405 --> 01:44:08,947
[Deadpool] Enjoy my Peter.

2492
