Not yet, it's not.

2497
01:44:40,072 --> 01:44:41,822
[Deadpool] Whoa. No, no, no.
We're very close.

2498
01:44:41,905 --> 01:44:43,322
Homestretch, folks. Promise.

2499
01:44:43,405 --> 01:44:44,988
Quick, let's up the stakes.

2500
01:44:45,072 --> 01:44:46,488
If she steals
the Time Ripper's energy,

2501
01:44:46,572 --> 01:44:49,072
she has the power to shred
the fabric of all realities

2502
01:44:49,155 --> 01:44:50,822
until there is nothing left
but The Void.

2503
01:44:50,905 --> 01:44:51,947
How do we shut it down?

2504
01:44:52,238 --> 01:44:53,280
I don't know.

2505
01:44:53,488 --> 01:44:54,488
[Mr. Paradox grunts]

2506
01:44:55,030 --> 01:44:56,197
[Wolverine] How about now?

2507
01:44:56,280 --> 01:44:57,572
[Deadpool] The mask
is really intimidating, huh?

2508
01:44:57,655 --> 01:44:59,738
It's like Batman,
except he can move his neck.

2509
01:44:59,822 --> 01:45:01,363
Okay, look, look, look.

2510
01:45:02,822 --> 01:45:05,238
The Ripper is fed from
a secure chamber below ground.

2511
01:45:05,322 --> 01:45:08,322
It is powered by twin matter
and anti-matter feeds

2512
01:45:08,405 --> 01:45:09,655
<i>converging inside the device.</i>

2513
01:45:09,738 --> 01:45:10,738
<i>Now, Cassandra Nova</i>

2514
01:45:10,822 --> 01:45:12,072
<i>is redirecting
the Ripper's power</i>

2515
01:45:12,155 --> 01:45:14,363
to eliminate all timelines,
starting with this one.

2516
01:45:14,447 --> 01:45:15,863
Theoretically,
you could stop her

2517
01:45:15,947 --> 01:45:17,863
by short-circuiting the feeds
in the chamber below.

2518
01:45:17,947 --> 01:45:20,405
One of you were to create a
circuit between the two feeds,

2519
01:45:20,488 --> 01:45:23,780
then the released power
would destroy the machine.

2520
01:45:23,863 --> 01:45:25,613
- But, well... But--
- [Deadpool] Come on, man.

2521
01:45:25,697 --> 01:45:27,780
If you're not gonna swallow,
spit it out.

2522
01:45:27,863 --> 01:45:30,988
Whoever formed the bridge
would be annihilated.

2523
01:45:31,072 --> 01:45:32,072
I could live with that.

2524
01:45:32,155 --> 01:45:33,155
[Deadpool] Yeah, I could live
with that, too, actually.

2525
01:45:33,238 --> 01:45:34,697
You know, we survive anything.
We're like cockroaches.

2526
01:45:34,780 --> 01:45:35,863
- [Deadpool chuckles]
- [Mr. Paradox] Not this time.

2527
01:45:35,947 --> 01:45:38,697
This is matter
and anti-matter.

2528
01:45:38,780 --> 01:45:40,780
They do not play nicely
with each other.

2529
01:45:40,863 --> 01:45:43,613
When they mix in your body,
you will be atomized.

2530
01:45:44,238 --> 01:45:46,280
Trust the laws of physics
if you don't trust me.

2531
01:45:46,363 --> 01:45:48,488
Even if you lived long enough
to make the circuit,

2532
01:45:48,572 --> 01:45:51,113
you will die down there.

2533
01:45:56,780 --> 01:45:57,947
[crackling]

2534
