[♪ dramatic choral
music playing]

2535
01:46:07,947 --> 01:46:09,197
[moaning]

2536
01:46:16,488 --> 01:46:17,905
[Wolverine] Hold off. Hold.

2537
01:46:17,988 --> 01:46:19,572
You heard
that asshole upstairs.

2538
01:46:19,655 --> 01:46:23,697
Even if we pull this off,
we're dead. Permanently.

2539
01:46:24,322 --> 01:46:26,363
- That's why it's got to be me.
- What?

2540
01:46:30,280 --> 01:46:31,572
Look, man... [panting]

2541
01:46:32,363 --> 01:46:34,113
you didn't ask
