I lied.

2544
01:46:37,905 --> 01:46:39,697
I lied right to your face

2545
01:46:39,780 --> 01:46:41,655
just to get you to help me.
And you did.

2546
01:46:42,572 --> 01:46:44,030
You didn't lie.

2547
01:46:46,030 --> 01:46:47,405
You made an educated wish.

2548
01:46:50,488 --> 01:46:51,488
Come on.

2549
01:46:52,738 --> 01:46:54,488
You got a whole world
to go back to.

2550
01:46:56,113 --> 01:46:57,113
I got nothin'.

2551
01:46:59,280 --> 01:47:00,280
I got nothin'.

2552
01:47:05,363 --> 01:47:06,363
Give me this.

2553
