Open the door!

2562
01:47:52,780 --> 01:47:55,572
[Deadpool] I can't hear you
over all the noble sacrifice.

2563
01:47:55,655 --> 01:47:56,780
Why are you
fucking doing this?

2564
01:47:57,197 --> 01:48:00,072
[Deadpool]
Because I'm Marvel Jesus.

2565
01:48:01,780 --> 01:48:02,780
Or Spock.

2566
