[exhales]

2590
01:49:24,447 --> 01:49:25,572
[continues straining]

2591
01:49:27,155 --> 01:49:28,655
He's not gonna make it.

2592
01:49:32,155 --> 01:49:33,363
[strains]

2593
01:49:37,363 --> 01:49:38,447
It's over.

2594
01:49:40,280 --> 01:49:41,280
[grunts]

2595
01:49:42,155 --> 01:49:43,322
[straining]

2596
